"Well, Gawen, which path will you take? The stealthy route proposed by the "
"underling, or the violent route proposed by the 'She-Wolf of Haeltin'?"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/17_Sneaking_out_of_Raedwood.cfg:410
